{"tid":2017955,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"甜心主播搞不倫被開除！近照曝光激瘦…連巨乳都哭到縮水","createTime":"2020-05-15T10:45:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T00:12:53.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d8089039dc9122687863b135771052926070d162","tid":2017955,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:45:25.000Z","msg":"日本前東京電視台的巨乳主播鷲見玲奈，在去年被踢爆偷偷摸摸跟已婚同事、主播增田和也有不正當男女關係，兩人在KTV偷情被抓包。電視台隨即將她打入冷宮，不僅勒令停工，3月底合約到期立刻就請她走人。鷲見玲奈在沉寂一段時間後，近日曝光近況，身型明顯瘦了一大圈，連傲人上圍都縮水了。<br />\n<br />\n據日媒報導，鷲見玲奈3月底在離開整整待了8年的東京電視台之後，對鏡頭變得十分敏感，外出時顯得相當緊張，一發現有人跟拍就匆匆躲避。原本經常更新的社群網站也中斷了好一陣子，不倫戀的曝光下場可說相當淒慘。好在鷲見玲奈憑著優異的外型條件，很快就找到新經紀事務所，無縫接軌成為自由主播。還有業界人士指出她可以靠拍清涼的性感寫真集翻身，人氣說不定會比現在更旺。<br />\n<br />\n鷲見玲奈11日在IG曬出30歲生日前夕時的自拍，只見她雖然五官依舊甜美，但整個人瘦了一圈，連傲人的招牌G罩杯都明顯縮水。對於外界的驚訝，鷲見玲奈則在13日的直播中，透露自己變瘦原因是因為被周刊記者糾纏追訪，家中外面經常停了很多腰跟拍的車輛，「很恐怖，就連吃飯都有麻煩，所以變瘦了」，但她或許怕惹麻煩，之後又在限時動態強調自己只是在節食減肥。"},{"pid":"b6d10f26112a92b7173733f8d744c2cecf0a7b7f","tid":2017955,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/15/2556157-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F15%2F2556157-XXL.jpg&h=687122c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼美女主播鷲見玲奈8年來累積高人氣。（圖／翻攝自鷲見玲奈IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/02/29/2432145-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F02%2F29%2F2432145-XXL.jpg&h=d90685b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"442385a3769d992a77a32aace15bdf2d4ec9098a","tid":2017955,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/15/2556150-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F15%2F2556150-XXL.jpg&h=1ce9cb46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼鷲見玲奈專業主播形象回不去，被看好拍清涼寫真集翻身。（圖／翻攝自鷲見玲奈IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/15/2556152-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F15%2F2556152-XXL.jpg&h=f0d255d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7fbcf55cf6de4025a78db24b51fdc6662b625f0","tid":2017955,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/15/2556159-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F15%2F2556159-XXL.jpg&h=8140f1d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼鷲見玲奈近況曝光，爆瘦一圈。（圖／翻攝自鷲見玲奈IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/15/2556158-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F15%2F2556158-XXL.jpg&h=1ae5bdb8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2110552b580999f8baa4edce42de0094c5164f73","tid":2017955,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T10:46:17.000Z","msg":"巨乳？？"},{"pid":"4a084eff721b18f63769936de0f278c7a2d51545","tid":2017955,"uid":35914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:16:15.000Z","msg":"我埋單算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700b3ba99d7c24516ac46c8b86ee92187f102905","tid":2017955,"uid":247518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:19:10.000Z","msg":"大波圖呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af501690f6a3d59fe5b90347aec06cb052de0713","tid":2017955,"uid":111814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:47:00.000Z","msg":"香港代表有周嘉儀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"422fd57552bf5560d4099c1f2ad9ff1c8ceb1793","tid":2017955,"uid":19217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T11:59:30.000Z","msg":"下海算啦<br />\n三上都老啦 有位上"},{"pid":"5bd